*"Otprilike znam kako bih to napravio." (roughly, I know how to do it.)

*"On je otprilike moje godine." (He is roughly my age.)

*"Razgovarali smo otprilike sat vremena." (We talked for roughly an hour.)

*"Otprilike znam gde je njen dom." (I roughly know where her house is.)

*"Svi smo otprilike u istoj situaciji." (We are all roughly in the same situation.)